rmal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而最好既抽籤情況 (賓狗+我島+不丹) 預計會有11.4分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最差既抽籤情況 (約旦+黎巴嫩+科威特/新加坡) 預測只係有3.5/5.5分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77dc43811d1cce17421acb8d0b997c4f08cab306","tid":27144,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:19:08.000Z","msg":"pot 4 關島一定難踢過馬拉同坡仔"},{"pid":"628c60778191fbf4433cef8ffc22b16abd44eeff","tid":27144,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:38:27.000Z","msg":"抽到賓狗+我島+不丹<br />\n同賓科 , 偉豪， 祖仔，村長屎水淋頭"},{"pid":"a55eb5ee30e22da804f232fa269bcd438f944bb2","tid":27144,"uid":38588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽到賓狗+我島+不丹<br />\n<br />\n同賓科 , 偉豪， 祖仔，村長屎水淋頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係驚D籤運上年已經用盡哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d151f185886458d77a6fcd2f78f7fd96e2070695","tid":27144,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽到賓狗+我島+不丹<br />\n同賓科 , 偉豪， 祖仔，村長屎水淋頭</blockquote><br />\ngun"},{"pid":"3dd4b3a30565cee80ad9358016cff5fcc049b96b","tid":27144,"uid":38588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"臭手第一下就抽到呢個組合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t1q798wr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft1q798wr&h=0aea76fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04889ffe46236255b357bf38296694cfe7a0ab4a","tid":27144,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抽到賓狗+我島+不丹<br />\n<br />\n同賓科 , 偉豪， 祖仔，村長屎水淋頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係驚D籤運上年已經用盡哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金仔d 狗屎